  <script type="text/javascript">
   // Çerez oluşturma
        function SetCookie(name, value, hours) {
            var expire = "";
            expire = new Date((new Date()).getTime() + hours * 3600000);
            expire = "; expires=" + expire.toGMTString();
            document.cookie = name + "=" + escape(value) + expire;
            return true;
        }

        // Cerez oku
        function GetCookie(name) {
            var cookieValue = "";
            var search = name + "=";
            if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
                offset = document.cookie.indexOf(search);
                if (offset != -1) {
                    offset += search.length;
                    end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", offset);
                    if (end == -1) end = document.cookie.length;
                    cookieValue = unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
                }
            }
            return cookieValue;
        }

        if (GetCookie('cerez') !== 'istanbulbarosu') {
            $(document).ready(function () {

                var id = '#pop-up-container-popup';
                //Get the screen height and width
                var maskHeight = $(document).height();
                var maskWidth = $(window).width();

                //Set heigth and width to mask to fill up the whole screen
                $('#overlayPopUp').css({ 'width': maskWidth, 'height': maskHeight });

                //transition effect
                $('#overlayPopUp').show();

                //Get the window height and width
                var winH = $(window).height();
                var winW = $(window).width();
                //transition effect
                $(id).show();

                setTimeout(function () {
                    $('#overlayPopUp').hide();
                    $(id).hide();
                    SetCookie('cerez', 'istanbulbarosu', 1);
                }, 10000);

                //if close button is clicked
                $('#close-popup-popup').click(function (e) {
                    //Cancel the link behavior
                    e.preventDefault();

                    $('#overlayPopUp').hide();
                    $(id).hide();
                    SetCookie('cerez', 'istanbulbarosu', 1);  // cerez olusturduk her ziyaretçiye bir kere açılması için
                });

                //if mask is clicked
                $('#overlayPopUp').click(function () {
                    $(this).hide();
                    $(id).hide();
                    SetCookie('cerez', 'istanbulbarosu', 1);// cerez olusturduk her ziyaretçiye bir kere açılması için
                });

            });
        }
  </script>
